::Kup/Rodimus Prime::

&quot;Rody, the other faction are bugging out, maybe we should retreat as well. Without the double attack we are greatly outnumbered. And with you injured...&quot;

Kup is cut off by Rodimus, &quot;Kup I saw him, he was here.&quot;

&quot;Saw who, lad?&quot; Asked Kup.

&quot;Galvatron. He was the one who injured me. He may have a new body, but it wasn&#39;t some Pred scum useing his name, it was the same Galvatron we fought so many years ago. I have to stop him...&quot;

&quot;Later, Roddy. Let&#39;s go home.&quot;

Kup activates his commlink to all Maximals.

&quot;This is Kup. The commander has been wounded and are advantage is gone. Pull back to base.&quot;

Kup transformes to truck mode, and uses a magnetic lock on Rodimus.

&quot;I&#39;ll pull you home, Roddy&quot;

Kup drives off, pulling Rodimus towards the base.

